Pacificio GARCIA, Appellant, v. A. C. SITTEL, U. S. Marshal for the Southern District of California, Appellee. No. 6357. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Jan. 12, 1931.

Before RUDKIN and WILBUR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

Ordered appeal dismissed pursuant to motion of appellant; mandate forthwith.
